headline: 2 Cash-Producing Stocks Worth Your Attention and 1 We Find Risky
summary: A company that generates cash isn’t automatically a winner. Some businesses stockpile cash but fail to reinvest wisely, limiting their ability to expand.

headline: Teledyne RESON Celebrates 50 Years of Acoustic Innovation
summary: SLANGERUP, Denmark, February 25, 2026--Teledyne Technologies Incorporated (NYSE:TDY) announced today that Teledyne Marine’s RESON brand, a name long synonymous with multibeam sonar, hydrophones, transducers and acoustic sensing, is celebrating its 50th anniversary in February. The milestone will be marked with new product unveilings and a special reception at Oceanology International (Oi26) on 10 March, where customers, partners and show attendees are invited to join the celebration.
